text: It a small japanese garden but the view is nice and beautiful
They could have created magic with these gardens.  But disappointed.  No shade and it was blah.   Not worth the visit

Very scenic and picturesque place with a serene and clear pond. There is many fishes inside swimming happily. There is also an arch bridge. Skilfully trimmed trees and bushes offer unique flora and fauna. A great pleasure walking through breathing in the fresh air. We enjoyed us thoroughly and would come again.
Nice place, with very big gardens.
